      "bio": "With extensive experience in the tourism sector, he leads AKMLEVA with the vision of turning every trip into a unique and personalized experience.",
      "fullBio": "Luís Campos is the heart and mind behind AKMLEVA. With more than 15 years dedicated to the tourism and real estate industry, he has built a solid reputation based on trust and excellence. His entrepreneurial vision made it possible to create an agency that does not merely sell destinations, but designs memories. As CEO, Luís is directly involved in strategic planning and in guaranteeing service quality, always maintaining the closeness with clients that defines the AKMLEVA brand.",
